    <briefdescription>
<para>Runtime tuning parameters for the free-body contact solver. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>These parameters control convergence and stability of the Projected Gauss-Seidel (Sequential Impulse) contact solve in SI units. For dense stacks, increasing iteration count and using moderate Baumgarte stabilization typically reduces jitter and drift. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
